This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4807

Tool to view the changes between your version and backed version or basis version.
There are four commands.
Ad      - View the difference between modified file and last kept file
Adbs  - View the difference between modified file and last updated version
Adbk  - View the difference between modified file and backed file in backed stream
Adc    - Exit the diff view
